    '<span style="color: #3b7600; font-weight:700;">Noncompetitive&nbsp;inhibitors</span> do NOT <span style="color: #a719db; font-weight:700;">bind</span>the <span style="color: #c80085; font-weight:700;">active site</span>, but can reduce <span style="color: #c80085; font-weight:700;">active site</span> activity.',
    '<span style="color: #3b7600; font-weight:700;">Noncompetitive&nbsp;inhibitors</span> <span style="color: #a719db; font-weight:700;">bind</span>to a site on the enzyme that is distinct from the <span style="color: #c80085; font-weight:700;">active site</span>',
